{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-documentation-tsx","path":"/zh/docs/handbook/nightly-builds.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"fc6afd42-7d70-5f58-abe5-2bd4014c43a5","excerpt":"在太平洋标准时间的每日午夜，TypeScript 代码仓库中master 分支上的代码会自动构建并发布到 npm 上。\n下面将介绍如何获取并结合你的工具来使用它。 使用 npm 更新 IDE 来使用每日构建 你还可以配置 IDE 来使用每日构建。\n首先你需要通过 npm…","html":"<p>在太平洋标准时间的每日午夜，TypeScript 代码仓库中<a href=\"https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/tree/master\">master 分支</a>上的代码会自动构建并发布到 npm 上。\n下面将介绍如何获取并结合你的工具来使用它。</p>\n<h2 id=\"使用-npm\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-npm\" aria-label=\"使用 npm permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用 npm</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki light-plus\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000\"><div class=\"language-id\">shell</div><div class='code-container'><code><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #000000\">npm install -g typescript@next</span></div></code></div></pre>\n<h2 id=\"更新-ide-来使用每日构建\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-ide-%E6%9D%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA\" aria-label=\"更新 ide 来使用每日构建 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>更新 IDE 来使用每日构建</h2>\n<p>你还可以配置 IDE 来使用每日构建。\n首先你需要通过 npm 来安装代码包。\n你可以进行全局安装或者安装到本地的<code>node_modules</code>目录下。</p>\n<p>在下面的内容中，我们假设你已经安装好了<code>typescript@next</code>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"visual-studio-code\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#visual-studio-code\" aria-label=\"visual studio code permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Visual Studio Code</h3>\n<p>参考以下示例来更新<code>.vscode/settings.json</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki light-plus\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000\"><div class=\"language-id\">json</div><div class='code-container'><code><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #A31515\">\"typescript.tsdk\"</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">: </span><span style=\"color: #A31515\">\"&lt;path to your folder&gt;/node_modules/typescript/lib\"</span></div></code></div></pre>\n<p>更多详情请参考 <a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/Docs/languages/typescript#_using-newer-typescript-versions\">VSCode 文档</a>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"sublime-text\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sublime-text\" aria-label=\"sublime text permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sublime Text</h3>\n<p>参考以下示例来更新<code>Settings - User</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki light-plus\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000\"><div class=\"language-id\">json</div><div class='code-container'><code><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #A31515\">\"typescript_tsdk\"</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">: </span><span style=\"color: #A31515\">\"&lt;path to your folder&gt;/node_modules/typescript/lib\"</span></div></code></div></pre>\n<p>更多详情请参考 <a href=\"https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript-Sublime-Plugin#installation\">如何在 Sublime Text 里安装 TypeScript 插件</a>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"visual-studio-2013-和-2015\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#visual-studio-2013-%E5%92%8C-2015\" aria-label=\"visual studio 2013 和 2015 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Visual Studio 2013 和 2015</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注意：绝大多数的变更不需要你安装新版本的 VS TypeScript 插件。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>目前，每日构建中没有包含完整的插件安装包，但是我们正在试着提供这样的安装包。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>下载 <a href=\"https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/blob/master/scripts/VSDevMode.ps1\">VSDevMode.ps1</a> 脚本。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>同时也可以参考 wiki 文档： <a href=\"https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/wiki/Dev-Mode-in-Visual-Studio#using-a-custom-language-service-file\">使用自定义的语言服务文件</a>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>打开 PowerShell 命令行窗口，并运行：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>针对 VS 2015：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki light-plus\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000\"><div class='code-container'><code>VSDevMode.ps1 14 -tsScript &lt;path to your folder&gt;/node_modules/typescript/lib</code></div></pre><!-- Note from shiki-twoslash: the language posh was not set up for Shiki to use, and so there is no code highlighting --!>\n<p>针对 VS 2013:</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki light-plus\" style=\"background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #000000\"><div class='code-container'><code>VSDevMode.ps1 12 -tsScript &lt;path to your folder&gt;/node_modules/typescript/lib</code></div></pre><!-- Note from shiki-twoslash: the language posh was not set up for Shiki to use, and so there is no code highlighting --!>\n<h3 id=\"intellij-idea-（mac）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intellij-idea-%EF%BC%88mac%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"intellij idea （mac） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IntelliJ IDEA （Mac）</h3>\n<p>前往 <code>Preferences</code> > <code>Languages &#x26; Frameworks</code> > <code>TypeScript</code>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>TypeScript Version：若通过 npm 安装则为：<code>/usr/local/lib/node_modules/typescript/lib</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"intellij-idea-（windows）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intellij-idea-%EF%BC%88windows%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"intellij idea （windows） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IntelliJ IDEA （Windows）</h3>\n<p>前往 <code>File</code> > <code>Settings</code> > <code>Languages &#x26; Frameworks</code> > <code>TypeScript</code>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>TypeScript Version：若通过 npm 安装则为：<code>C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\typescript\\lib</code></p>\n</blockquote>","headings":[{"value":"使用 npm","depth":2},{"value":"更新 IDE 来使用每日构建","depth":2},{"value":"Visual Studio Code","depth":3},{"value":"Sublime Text","depth":3},{"value":"Visual Studio 2013 和 2015","depth":3},{"value":"IntelliJ IDEA （Mac）","depth":3},{"value":"IntelliJ IDEA （Windows）","depth":3}],"frontmatter":{"permalink":"/zh/docs/handbook/nightly-builds.html","title":"每日构建","disable_toc":null,"handbook":null,"oneline":"如何使用TypeScript的每日构建版本","preamble":null,"deprecated_by":null,"deprecation_redirects":null,"experimental":null}},"prev":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"8-每日构建","slug":"/zh/docs/handbook/nightly-builds.html","repoPath":"/packages/documentation/copy/zh/Nightly Builds.md","lang":"zh","modifiedTime":"2024-10-21T12:35:09.573Z"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}